[normal]Written evidence submitted by [bold]The West London Housing Partnership[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The West London Housing Partnership[bold] is an umbrella organisation for the 7 West London Local Housing Authorities of Brent; Ealing; Hammersmith &amp;
[normal] Fulham; Harrow; Hillingdon; Hounslow, and the Royal Borough of Kensington and 
[normal]Chelsea
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]WLHP is committed to managing the effects of Welfare Reform but also recognises the burdens and pressures that have been placed on local authorities, social landlords 
[normal]and residents. . 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We draw your attention to 
[normal]the London-
[normal]specific issues raised in this report in the hope that they will add some weight to the case for reconsideration of 
[normal]London
[normal]’s unique situation under this legislation.
[normal]&#xa0;
