[normal]llowance
[normal] and
[normal] benefit caps have led to an increase in homeless approaches from people evicted from private rented accommodation
[normal]. L
[normal]oss of private rented 
[normal]accommodation 
[normal]is now the biggest single cause of homelessness
[normal] and has created a huge increase in pressure on local authorities
